        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Compassionate Assistance for Parents with Children with Special Needs Act of 2004 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide that the medical expenses of disabled children under the age of 18 shall be tax deductible without regard to the 7.5 percent adjusted gross income threshold .</p>]]></text>
